        "TileImage": "$($repository e1c8c0a5-a506-45b6-9567-7b6df50b8877).Image",
        "Description": "The information we received from the locals of Ambrose was regarding Omar Al-Ghazali, the owner of the recently built Spire skyscraper in Dubai. Our client&apos;s reputation was ruined by an article exposing their affair after they refused to agree to Omar&apos;s terms on a real-estate deal. The article was published anonamously but one of the locals who contracted us to kill Farah was a cybersecurity expert who was able to identify the writer as Journalist Hans Lucht, a secret acquitance of Omar.",
